title: [Teras Isle, Fhorian Village]
description: A horrible stench pervades the air here.  The pungent odor overcomes even the strong smell of cinders and burnt wood that has been pervalent throughout the rest of the village.  There is no obvious source for the smell, but whatever it is must be nearby.
